  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients will be asked to use a mobile phone app to conduct their hand therapy after having
      hand surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients who are undergoing the included procedures will be informed of the study &amp;
      consented. They will be given information on how to download the app &amp; input their surgery
      date. The app will guide the patient through various hand therapy exercises and ask them to
      record their QuickDASH, PSFS and VAS Pain weekly.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
